message.body: How do u wanna get this camera? I could drop it by on my way outta town tomorrow late morning. Or you could get it from my roommate whenever.
Oh man! Thanks for letting me borrow it! I will be home tmw!
I can pick it up from you too, just let me know what time
I'll be driving, so I can drop it off. Maybe around 10 or 11am on my way out of town.
Perfect. Thank you so much. You are the best!!!
I'm still packing. Probably get to yours closer to noon.
